Solly Makganoto Johannesburg –  ANC Women’s League president Bathabile Dlamini has urged all women protect themselves and their loved ones during this festive season. Dlamini was speaking in a video in which she appealed women to protect their children from child trafficking, child snatchers and accidents. “The time has come for us as women to ensure that we are safe at all times and we must tell our men that real men do not abuse women, real men do not rape women, they respect women,” said Dlamini in a video. Watch the full video below: